title: Introduction | Vagrant | HashiCorp Developer
excerpt: Vagrant is a tool for building complete development environments. With an easy-to-use workflow and focus on automation, Vagrant lowers development environment setup time, increases development/production parity, and makes the "it works on my machine" excuse a relic of the past.

title: Quick Start | Vagrant | HashiCorp Developer
excerpt: Vagrant isolates dependencies and their configuration within a single disposable and consistent development environment.
